td class=\"tg-c3ow\">iv)</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-0pky\">H<sub>2</sub>S in presence of NH<sub>4</sub>OH</td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></p>\n<p>Correct match is -</p>",
